snippet.title: MUTTON OMELETTE | Eggs with Whole Goat Meat | High Protein Omelette Recipe | Healthy Breakfast
snippet.description:
Enjoy a healthy, high-protein start to your day with this Mutton Omelette made using eggs and whole goat meat. Cooked in traditional village style, this recipe blends soft steamed mutton with fluffy eggs — perfect for muscle gain, weight loss, and low-carb diets.

If you love natural cooking, protein-rich meals, and authentic rural food, this video is for you!

snippet.title: Chahvan Sohneya - Danny | Madhubanti Bagchi | Rohit Zinjurke | Roshni Walia | New Punjabi Song 2025
snippet.description:
Chahvan Sohneya is a heartfelt and soulful track sung by Danny and Madhubanti Bagchi, capturing the way love is expressed in today’s world. Featuring the charming Rohit Zinjurke and glamorous Roshni Walia, the video brings the emotions to life with their chemistry and stunning visuals. Directed by the legendary Rupan Bal, this song is a perfect blend of emotion, music, and visual beauty — a true treat for the heart and soul.

snippet.title: Koi Naa | Bhool Chuk Maaf | Rajkummar Rao, Wamiqa Gabbi | Tanishk, Irshad, Shreya, Harnoor, Gifty
snippet.description:
Sang tere rehna khayal banke,
Aati mujhe duji tarqeeb koi na!
 
Presenting the first song release ‘Koi Naa’ from ‘Bhool Chuk Maaf’, featuring Rajkummar Rao and Wamiqa Gabbi! Composed by Tanishk Bagchi and Gifty, it is sung by Harnoor and Shreya Ghoshal and penned by Irshad Kamil. Perfect to dedicate to someone who’s a romantic, let this speak the words of your heart to that special someone!
 
#KoiNaa #ShreyaGhoshal #Harnoor #TanishkBagchi #Gifty #irshadKamil #RajkummarRao #WamiqaGabbi #BhoolChukMaaf
 
Song credits:
Title : Koi Naa
Singers : Harnoor & Shreya Ghoshal
Composers : Tanishk Bagchi & Gifty
Music Production : Tanishk Bagchi & Ganesh Waghela
Lyricist : Irshad Kamil
Language : Hindi
Mix Master : Eric Pillai @ Future sound of Bombay
Assistant Mix Engineer : Michael Edwin Pillai
Original Punjabi Music & Lyrics : Gifty
Original Song Licensed by Jatt Life Studios
 
Maddock Films presents #BhoolChukMaaf
In cinemas on 9th May
Cast: Rajkummar Rao, Wamiqa Gabbi, Sanjay Mishra, Seema Pahwa, Zakir Hussain, Raghubir Yadav, Ishtiyak Khan, Anubha Fatehpuria
Produced By: Dinesh Vijan
Directed By: Karan Sharma
Co-Producers: Sharada Karki Jalota
Music By: Tanishk Bagchi
Background Score: Ketan Sodha
Story Screenplay & Dialogues By: Karan Sharma
Director Of Photography: Sudeep Chatterjee
Lyrics: Irshad Kamil
Director of Choreography: Vijay A Ganguly
 
Lyrics:

Yaara mere dil ke kareeb koi na
Tere siva apna naseeb koi na
Sang tere rehna khayal banke
Aati mujhe duji tarqeeb koi na
 
Kehta hai tujhko haseen aaina
Tujh mein hi rehta hai leen aaina
Bolo isey mujhko jalaya na kare
Lena maine tujhse ye chheen aaina
 
Mujhse hi sun le tareef apni
Shaadi wali milti lakeer apni
Teri meri duniya basegi jis mein
Aane wali jaldi tareekh apni

Tu to mere surmey jaisa
Tu to mere sapne jaisa
Akhiyon Mein
Rakhna hai
Sabse chhupa ke tujhko
Chupke se
Marzi se
Chaahungi  tujhko

Yaara mere dil ke kareeb koi na
Tere siva apna naseeb koi na
Sang tere rehna khayal banke
Aati mujhe duji tarqeeb koi na

Dilon ki ameeri mein gareeb koi na
Ashiqon se badh ke ajeeb koi na
Aankhein milein jab tab Jaan pe baney
Ishqey se oonchi to saleeb koi na
 
(Tere jaisa ik mera Yaar aaina
Chadhti jawani ka shingaar aaina
Dekho mujhe kitna guroor ho gaya
Leke aayin mujhpe nikhaar aaina)

Chura le mujhe ab Sajjana tu saara
Jawani tere naam kar di maine yaara
Laga ke tujhe honth se apne dekhun
Kahan se tu m meetha kahan se khaara

Paaniyon pe behte chiraag jaisi tu
Mehke gulaabon ke hai baag jaisi tu
Thandi hoti akkhiyann tujhe dekh ke
Chhooney se to lagti hai aag jaisi tu
 
Yaara mere dil ke kareeb koi na
Tere siva apna naseeb koi na
Sang tere rehna khayal banke
Aati mujhe duji tarqeeb koi na

Tera mera ek jaisa haal ho gaya
Dooriyon mein rahna mohaal ho gaya
Le ke aaja jaldi. Baraat maahiya
Rang meri menhdi ka laal ho gaya
 
Tu to mere surmey jaisa
Tu to mere sapne jaisa
Akhiyon Mein
Rakhna hai
Sabse chhupa ke tujhko
Chupke se
Marzi se
Chaahungi  tujhko

Yaara mere dil ke kareeb koi na
Tere siva apna naseeb koi na
Sang tere rehna khayal banke
Aati mujhe duji tarqeeb koi na

Main tere pe mar gayi sajna re
Tu samjha na
Ishq se main bhar gayi sajna re
Tu samjha na
Tere aage peechhe ghoomti phirun
Piye bina hi main jhoomti phirun
Tere saaye ko bhi choomti phirun
Meri jaan
Tujhpe nisaar sajna

Yaara mere dil ke kareeb koi na
Tere siva apna naseeb koi na
Sang tere rehna khayal banke
Aati mujhe duji tarqeeb koi na

Academy Award®-winning director Danny Boyle and Academy Award®-nominated writer Alex Garland reunite for 28 Years Later, a terrifying new story set in the world created by 28 Days Later. It’s been almost three decades since the rage virus escaped a biological weapons laboratory, and now, still in a ruthlessly enforced quarantine, some have found ways to exist amidst the infected. One such group of survivors lives on a small island connected to the mainland by a single, heavily-defended causeway. When one of the group leaves the island on a mission into the dark heart of the mainland, he discovers secrets, wonders, and horrors that have mutated not only the infected but other survivors as well.

ఒలల్లా, 
చూపుల్తో గుచ్చి గుచ్చి చంపకే మేరే హాయ్

గుండెల్ని గుల్ల చేసి జారకే, మేరే హాయ్

ఒలల్ల, 
నీ ప్రేమ కోసం నేను పిచ్చోన్నైపోయానే
నీ ప్రేమ కోసం నేను పిచ్చోన్నైపోయానే

હે જોઈ હૈયુ રે હિબકાઈ ગયુ મારા દલડા રે દુભાણા
એ મને દુઃખી જોઈ પોપણ એના પણ ભીજાણા
હો હો હેડવુ મારે થઈ ગયુ ત્યાથી પગ મારો ના ઉપડે
ઘડી ઘડી નજર મારી એના હોમી ઉપડે
હે મારો પ્યાર મારો રહ્યો નથી પુરી બીજા મન મડી પોખી...(૨)
હે રોમ રોમ માં લાય લાગી અંદર અંદર હુ બળ્યો 
દુઃખ થયુ દિલ માં ઘણું પણ કઈ બોલી ના શકયો
હે સાસરે થી આયા પિયાર માં હારે પતિ ને જોયો...(૨)

હે તમે સાસરે જાશો તમારા અમે દુઃખ માં દાઝતા રેશુ
રોઇ રોઇ રાતો ઘાઢશુ પણ કોઇ ના કેશુ
હે તારા નામ ની હૈયા બળતરા મને કોટા ની જેમ વાગે
તુ પારકા ની પરણેતર તારા પર હક ના મારો લાગે
હે લખાયુ હસે થવાનુ રે જુદા યાદ આવશે તારી સદા...(૨)
હે એની આશા છોડી દિધી રોઈ રદો રે વાળ્યો
દુઃખી રઈશુ આખી જીંદગી નહિ મળે સુખ નો છાયો
હે સાસરે થી આયા પિયાર માં હારે પતિ ને જોયો...(3)

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy:

Daya learns from Tapu that he cannot locate Bapuji in Paris.  Daya informs Jethalal that Tapu is unable to locate Bapuji in Paris, and Jethalal immediately heads to Gada House.  Will Tapu be able to locate Bapuji?  Will Tapu and Bapuji cross paths?

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 578
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2025 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Comedy Episodes' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cS1vnURTBH_Bt7xdxb2el1d

Experience the divine beauty of Vrindavan with the video of “Pyaro Vrindavan” — a heartfelt tribute to love, devotion, and the eternal connection between the soul and the divine.

Let the music transport you to the sacred lanes of Vrindavan, where every note echoes with bhakti and every frame radiates spiritual grace. This is more than just a song — it’s a journey into the heart of devotion.

"Kripa Records" is a devotional music label dedicated to producing and promoting spiritual music that inspires profound experiences. पोर कट्यार...

चटक चांदनी, लई गोजिरी..
छबिदार गुलजार..
लई ग्वाड ही ऊसावानी रं..
घोर जीवा आहे रं..

लई देखनी, हरनीवानी..
पोरं ही अंगार..
घोर लाविती, याड लाविती..
पिरमाचा काहूर..

ठावं नाही जी काही..
सैरंभैरं म्या झालो..
जीव वतून गेलं.. 
तुझ्या नादातं..

दिलाची धडधड..
व्हटावं आली रं..
पोराचा बाजार उठला रं..

(अंतरा)

मन येडं बघ झालं..
रानी तुझ्या मागं..
केसात तुझ्या वारं..
फिरतंया भारी गं..

रातीला झोप नाही..
भूक नाही, तानभी गं..
पूनवाचा तू चांद..
मी रात झालो गं..

नजरनं ठार कर तू..
नजरनं लाज तू..
चांदनं टिपूर तू..
नजरनं ठार कर तू..

ठावं नाही जी काही..
सैरंभैरं म्या झालो..
जीव वतून गेलं.. 
तुझ्या नादातं..

दिलाची धडधड..
व्हटावं आली रं..
पोराचा बाजार उठला रं..

snippet.title: Are Companies Cheating Us? | Dreamz Unlimited | Consumer Protection
snippet.description:
How Can a Customer Fight for Their Rights?
Every customer has the right to safety, information, choice, and redressal. But what can you do when these rights are violated? Here's how a customer can fight for their rights:
Know Your Rights - First, be aware of your basic consumer rights — such as the right to be informed, the right to choose, the right to safety, and the right to seek redressal.
Keep Proof - Always keep receipts, bills, warranty cards, emails, or any communication related to the product or service. These documents act as evidence if a complaint needs to be raised.
Talk to the Seller - In many cases, simply raising the issue with the shop or service provider politely can solve the problem.
File a Formal Complaint - If the seller refuses to help, you can file a complaint with: Department of Legal Metrology & Consumer Protection
(Respective States)
Use Social Media - Tagging companies on social platforms like Twitter or Instagram often gets their attention quickly. Many companies take online reputation seriously.
Take Legal Action - If needed, you can approach a consumer court. These courts are specially set up to handle consumer disputes in a quicker and more affordable manner.
This video is produced by
Department of Legal Metrology & Consumer Protection
Govt. of Nagaland

snippet.title: क्यों हमे जीते जी मार डालना चाहती हैं Prem Granth Movie Scene - Madhuri - Sulbha Arya - Om Puri
snippet.description:
Prem Granth is a 1996 Hindi romantic bollywood drama film starring Rishi Kapoor, Madhuri Dixit, Anupam Kher and Om Puri. The story revolves around Somen, son a Hindu priest of the village. Somen falls in love with Kajri who belongs to a lower caste and Somen’s family disapprove their relationship. When Kajri goes missing, Somen leaves his village to stay with his uncle. Will the lovers ever reunite?

💎 Movie : Prem Granth - प्रेम ग्रन्थ (1996)
💎 Director: Rajiv Kapoor - राजीव कपूर 
💎 Cast: 
    Shammi Kapoor - शम्मी कपूर as Nandlal
    Rishi Kapoor - ऋषि कपूर as Somen
    Madhuri Dixit - माधुरी दीक्षित as Kajri
    Anupam Kher - अनुपम खेर as Swami Dharam Bhooshan
    Om Puri - ओम पूरी as Baliram
    Prem Chopra - प्रेम चोपड़ा as Kedar Nath
    Reema Lagoo - रीमा लागू as Parvati
    Himani Shivpuri as Natho
    Sulabha Arya as Laxmi
    Govind Namdeo as Roop Sahai
💎 Music : Laxmikant–Pyarelal - लक्ष्मीकांत - प्यारेलाल 


#rishikapoor #madhuri #shammikapoor #anupamkher #romantic #latest #90s #90severgreen

snippet.title: Masala Bread Toast Recipe in Tamil | Bread Recipes in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video, we will see how to make Masala Bread Toast recipe in Tamil. This spicy and flavorful bread toast is the perfect option for a quick breakfast, evening snack, or even a light dinner. Loaded with sautéed vegetables and simple spices, this toast is crispy on the outside and packed with delicious masala flavor on the inside. This Masala Bread Toast is a street-style favorite that can be made easily at home with pantry staples. It’s a fantastic way to transform plain bread into a satisfying dish that’s sure to please both kids and adults. The combination of soft veggies, a hint of spice, and buttery toasted bread makes it irresistible every single time. Whether you're running late for work or just want a quick and easy meal, this recipe will come in handy. You can customize the masala to your taste and even add cheese for an extra treat. Serve it hot with ketchup or chutney and enjoy the comforting flavors of this quick and easy toast.
#masalabread #breadtoastrecipe #breadrecipeintamil 

Friends, please do try this Masala Bread Toast recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!

Ingredients:
Makes 6 paneer masala bread toast
1/4 cup Chickpea flour
1/4 cup Rice flour
1/2 Onion
Curry leaves
Coriander leaves
1/2 tsp Ginger paste
1 Green Chilli
1/4 tsp Garam masala
1/2 tsp Coriander powder
1/2-3/4 tsp Chilli powder
1 tsp Sesame seeds
1/2 cup grated Paneer
Salt as required
Water as required
Oil (3-4 tsp / slice)

Episode 4373: Cricket Ka Bhoot
--------------------------------------------------------
With cricket season in full swing, excitement fills the air. Tapu Sena gears up for the match while Gogi and Tapu raise the stakes with a playful pizza bet. Which team will come out on top?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Dakat Poreche | ডাকাত পড়েছে | Aarii | Iman Chakraborty | Srabanti C | Yash D | Nussrat J | Keshab D
snippet.description:
যশ দাশগুপ্ত, নুসরত ও মৌসুমী চট্টোপাধ্যায় অভিনীত নতুন ছবি "আড়ি" সিনেমার একটি মজাদার ও ছন্দময়  নতুন গান "ডাকাত পড়েছে"! গানে কণ্ঠ দিয়েছেন জাতীয় পুরস্কারপ্রাপ্ত গায়িকা ইমন চক্রবর্তী, যাঁর জাদুকরী কণ্ঠ আর দুর্দান্ত স্টাইল নিয়ে এসেছে একেবারে নতুন মাত্রা।

Get ready to groove to the bold and vibrant beats of "Dakat Poreche", the sensational item song from the much-awaited Bengali film "Aarii"! Sung with power and style by the National Award-winning singer Iman Chakraborty, this track is packed with energy, attitude, and irresistible rhythm

snippet.title: Gokuldham के Gents को क्यों पहननी पड़ी साड़ी?| Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | 14 Apr 2025
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Jetha finds himself in a tricky situation one side is his wife and another side his best friend on whose victory he should be happy. Daya wins the arm wrestling and Jetha claps and appreciates her. Jetha and Sundar come face to face for arm wrestling and Jetha wins. All first-round winners go into the second round. Jetha and Champak face each other in arm wrestling and Champak wins. We see Komal and Goli one by one win overall contestants. In the end, Dr. Hathi and Popatlal come against each other for arm wrestling.


Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 632
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.description:
Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. snippet.title: Chaurya Paatam Official Trailer -Indhra Ram,Payal Radhakrishna-Nikhil Gollamari-ThrinadhaRao Nakkina
snippet.description:
Watch and enjoy the official trailer of #ChauryaPaatam is an crime comedy-drama film featuring Indhra Ram and Payal Radhakrishna in the lead roles. snippet.title: Rong Oi Rongali - Achurjya Borpatra | Sunit Gogoi | Pankaj Bora | New Bihu 2025
snippet.description:
Presenting official audio of #AchurjyaBorpatra's #RongOiRongali  (#AssameseSong) exclusively on Achurjya Borpatra Official.

"ৰঙ ঐ ৰঙালী" 
কণ্ঠ : আচুৰ্য বৰপাত্ৰ 
কথা - সুৰ - সংগীত পৰিচালনা : শোণিত গগৈ, পংকজ বৰা 
শব্দ সংমিশ্ৰণ : দিগন্ত বৰদলৈ 
সহযোগী কণ্ঠ : জনম কাশ্যপ, ৰাগদীপ চেতিয়া 
বাদ্য শিল্পী : 
ঢোল : পংকজ বৰা,লাচিত বৰুৱা,অংকুৰ বুঢ়াগোহাঁই 
তাল-পেঁপা-গগণা-ধূতং :
পিটি বৰা 
বাঁহী : কৈলাশ ৰাভা 
বাণীবন্ধন কক্ষ : ষ্টুডিঅ' অ'ডিঅহলিক 
বাণীবদ্ধক : স্বপ্নিল দত্ত, নিখিলেশ বৰা 
বিশেষ কৃতজ্ঞতা : বিশাল মহন বৰা, অভিনন্দন বৰা, প্ৰাণজিত নাথ 
হুঁচৰিটোৰ কিছু কথাংশ পৰম্পৰাগত ।

Label: AB Production
Music Publisher: Eikhon Axom Hoi Bhai Media

© ℗ 2025 Achurjya Borpatra Official. All Rights Reserved.

Mehshar Episode 37 - [Eng Sub] - Imran Abbas - Neelam Muneer - 17th April 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated project, Mehshar, reunites the beloved on-screen duo of Imran Abbas and Neelam Muneer in a tale of love that promises to leave a mark on the viewers!

In Mehshar, love meets sacrifice as it follows the journey of a person who adores someone whose ambitions surpass all, leaving love behind. This is a story where love is selfless and giving is what matters most.

The story revolves around Abdur Rehman and Aima, cousins bound by a twist of fate. Their journey is not just about love, it’s about the emotions and sacrifices that truly make their bond special.

Is Abdur Rehman and Aima’s love destined to last forever, or will tragedy destroy it? Will their sacrifices and emotions elevate love to new heights? Will ambitions overpower love in this tale?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: ভূতরাজ্যে নববর্ষ | Gopal Bhar | Episode - 1143
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to SONY AATH Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBz9qbqujcjIavFmBJW2oZw?sub_confirmation=1

Maharaj dreams of a grand New Year celebration and plans something special for everyone. Will everything go as planned?

Show Name: Gopal Bhar - গোপালভাঁড়
Directed By: Sourav Mondal, Hansa Mondal
Written By: Hansa Mondal
Original language: Bengali
Episode No: 1143

#GopalBhar #sonyaath #গোপালভর 

About Gopal Bhar:
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him as a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers.

snippet.title: ஒரு கப் ரசம் போதும், வேற எதுவும் வேணாம்! Tomato Rasam This Tasty? Chef Deena's Kitchen
snippet.description:
Kalyana Veetu Rasam
Ready to unlock the secret to that irresistible wedding rasam? Chef Deena is on a mission, and he's teamed up with Chennai's very own young culinary whiz, Mr. Harish from Janani Catering Services in West Mambalam!  Get ready to learn the nuances of an aromatic and flavorful rasam recipe, a staple at South Indian weddings, as Mr. Harsh guides us through the step-by-step process. Let's dive in and discover the magic of Janani Catering's Kalyanam Rasam! 

Sri Janani Catering Service
Mr. Harish
Contact : 9840703703

கல்யாண வீட்டு ரசம் | Kalyaana Veettu Rasam (Wedding-Style Rasam)
Thakkali Rasam
Tomato - 1 Kg
Mustard - 1 Tsp
Cumin Seeds - 1 Tsp
Pepper - 35 g
Asafoetida - 1 Tsp
Tamarind - 100 g
Jaggerry - 1/2 Tsp
Chrushed Garlic - 100 g
Dry Red Chilli - 6 to 7 Nos 
Green Chilli - 6 to 7 Nos
Curry Leaves - As Required 
Coriander Leaves - As Required 
Turmeric Powder - 1/2 Tsp
Salt - To Taste 
Gingelly Oil - 200 ml 
Ghee - For Tempering
 


My Amazon Store { My Picks and Recommended Product }
https://www.amazon.in/shop/chefdeenaskitchen

_______________
Hello!!  My Name is chef Deena from the popular Adupangarai show in Jaya TV Viewers must have seen me in Zee Tamil shows as well.  My Culinary journey as a trainee to become an Executive Chef is incredible. My experience in the culinary field is for more than fifteen years and my USP is Indian cooking !! Apart from being a TV cookery host, my experience lies mainly with being employed in some of the major star hotels across the country especially the Marriott group.

     Chef Deena Cooks is my English Youtube Channel! Practical, simple recipes are my forte and using minimal easily available ingredients is my hallmark. Rudiments of cooking and baking are taught from scratch and any amateur cook can learn to make exciting dishes by watching my channel!  Also, Cooking traditional foods, Easy cooking Recipes, Healthy Snacks, Indian curries, gravies, Baking and Millions of other homemade treats. 

Subscribe to Chef Deena Cooks (CDK) for more cooking videos.
